{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1654078131.4922013", "card_id": "Q_535392590", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 254}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "因荷兰拒绝通过卢布结算天然气费用，俄罗斯宣布停供荷兰天然气，会带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间周一，俄罗斯天然气股份有限公司（下称「俄气」）在官网宣布，因荷兰拒绝通过卢布结算天然气费用的要求，自 5 月 31 日起停止向该国输送天然气。 来源：第一财经"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-5d691b35177c891e93b56047340cad44_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "656 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/535392590"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9N2hxJbm37hBEAMaCDgxMjU4Mjk1IMzn1ZQGMCg4+gZAAHIJNTM1MzkyNTkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1654078131.493664", "card_id": "Q_535621535", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 560}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "6 月 1 日四川雅安市芦山县附近发生 6.1 级地震，目前情况如何？你那里震感强吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国地震台网正式测定：06 月 01 日 17 时 00 分在四川雅安市芦山县（北纬 30.37 度，东经 102.94 度）发生 6.1 级地震，震源深度 17 千米。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-65bfe68b17ca88415b7dbc2c02cf1c2e_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "634 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/535621535"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI9N2hxJbm37hBEAMaCDgxMzA5MDQ4INjX3JQGMDs4+gZAAXIJNTM1NjIxNTM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1654078131.495096", "card_id": "Q_535549507", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 464}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "上海全面恢复全市正常生产生活秩序的第一天，你是怎么度过的？有哪些不得不说的故事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-15a1b2aff2646339a7d04c82f7c1a542_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text